{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676430/extras/text1.png?t=1729278025\" />Convicted is a survival horror multiplayer game set in a top-secret Soviet facility during the 1980s, full of unethical experiments, paranormal activities, and dangerous monsters! An accident happened to free some of the lab's anomalies, which will hunt you down! Play as them or try to escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676430/extras/Convicted_-_Anomaly_attacks.gif?t=1729278025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676430/extras/text2.png?t=1729278025\" />Explore the secret Soviet laboratory, and be sure not to miss any items. They could potentially save your life! After all, you don't really know how to stop the strange, hostile anomalies. Will ordinary firearms be able to stop them? Well, there's only one way to find that out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676430/extras/Convicted_-_Equipment.gif?t=1729278025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676430/extras/text3.png?t=1729278025\" />Your main goal is to escape from the facility. However, you'll face plenty of obstacles in your attempt to do so, from opposing human forces to the environmental hazards of the lab itself! Always be on alert, and be sure to keep checking behind you. <strong>Trust no one.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676430/extras/Convicted_-_PvP.gif?t=1729278025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.st